Start or switch to Bash:startbash.sh
Stop Bash:stopbash.sh force
Restart Bash:restartbash.sh force
List all available options for Bash:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Bash
View the current value of Bash option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Bash -g
View the current value of Bash option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Bash -g -r
Change the value of read-write Bash option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Bash -s
Change the value of read-write Bash option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Bash -s -r
Display help for Bash option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Bash -d
Display help for Bash option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Bash -d -r
Display TTY currently allocated to Bash:confapps_ph.sh -p tty -a Bash
Move Bash to another TTY:confapps_ph.sh -p move -a Bash -t prompt
Return to previous menu:return
